{"tid":999191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果在中美推iPhone新政策：以舊換新+分期付款","createTime":"2019-01-28T13:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T14:47:19.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0789256529bb190e8745e3e550095de9f463ba70","tid":999191,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"據騰訊科技， 北京時間周三早間，蘋果公司將發布去年第四季度的財報。iPhone銷售低迷成為外界對蘋果財報最大關注焦點。據外媒最新消息，在財報發布之前，蘋果公司又推出了一個十分罕見的手機促銷政策，向用舊iPhone購買iPhone XS或iPhone XR的客戶提供每月分期付款選項。蘋果在美國和中國的蘋果商店推出了新的月度分期付款選項。不過，每月付款優惠在歐洲的蘋果商店上是不可用的"},{"pid":"6b645e80d7a55519dfc93e8754c63021243ec099","tid":999191,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6ae4f38dc4e253cc3212aad0b0c6732b228d98","tid":999191,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"冇XS Max<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf7820822f98a5f264e7e8ba7f0952c44412e02","tid":999191,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:01:18.000Z","msg":"減價好過啦搞咁多野"},{"pid":"5697ce8079c138148ffed909f9b9cbeb2120ba2e","tid":999191,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:02:12.000Z","msg":"推到買1送1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9d4abf5b16e46df9a3bf0379139e71583bbba8","tid":999191,"uid":168366,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">減價啦仆街<br />\n死gay cook今年所有產品都貴過以前</span>"},{"pid":"d16a64c4d5af2c65706a32305af4f8424f91f0f0","tid":999191,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"r